<ol>
  <li>You do not talk about Blog Club.</li>
  <li><strong>You do not talk about Blog Club.</strong></li>
  <li>Someone yells “Stop!”, goes limp, taps out, the Blog is over.</li>
  <li>Only two writers to a Blog.</li>
  <li>One blog at a time, fellas.</li>
  <li>No shirts, no shoes.</li>
  <li>Blogs will go on as long as they have to.</li>
  <li>Final rule: If this is your first night at Blog Club, you have to Blog.</li>
</ol>

